reviews.review_text: funky Just got thru with this one, and can't stop boppin' my head and humming "When I Paint My Masterpiece". It really grooves begining to end. Love It.

High-Altitude Dead I'll never forget these shows because of the rumors surrounding how Jerry would handle the altitude.  To say the least: He handled it great! The weekend shows were happening the same weekend as the Harmonic Convergence , and the vibe the whole weekend was incredible.  Both shows were great, but this Sunday afternoon show was the better of the two.  Still gives me goosebumps!
